  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong><br />Gardens by the Bay<br /></p><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br />• Provide information and assistance to visitors<br />• Ensure ticket and attraction admission checks<br />• Handling of crowd control<br />• Assist to facilitate events and programmes held<br /></p><p></p><p><strong>Working Hour:</strong><br />Required to work at least 3 days a week for minimum 3 months<br />8.30am - 9.30pm (6-12 hour rotating shifts)<br /></p><p></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong><br />During peak period of 13 Feb – 1 Mar 2026, the salary is</p><p>$14/h weekdays</p><p>$16/h weekends<br /></p><p>For the rest of the dates, the salary is</p><p>$10/h weekdays</p><p>$12/h weekends<br /></p><p></p><p>Thank you!<br /></p><p>Toh Kim Leng (Glendon)<br />Cornerstone Global Partners<br />EA: 19C9859<br />Reg no: R1982182</p>",
